      <title>由於市場權衡強勁的薪資數據和聯準會會議，華爾街股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-drift-lower-focus-shifts-rate-verdict-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國股市週二收低，因市場權衡顯示勞動成本上升和消費者信心惡化的經濟數據，聯準會將在決定利率方向的重要政策會議當天召開。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-drift-lower-focus-shifts-rate-verdict-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
